PrecisEnactment of the OIL POLLUTION PREVENTION REGULATIONS which are designed to protect our territorial waters from damage caused by oil pollution originating from maritime shipping operations, and revoke the current Regulations of the same name and the Non-Canadian Ships Compliance Certificate Regulations, effective February 16, 1993.
